data.title: St. John the Baptist Catholic Church
data.meta_description: St. John the Baptist Catholic Church - Resources page
data.meta_site_name: St. John the Baptist Catholic Church
data.text:
There are several resources for todays catholics.

Applications that are worth installing in your smartphone:

- Laudate. This is an application that has several resources in one place. Laudate has prayers, the daily readings, Rosary, Chaplet of Divine Mercy, Stations of the Cross and more. This is a free application.

- iBreviary. This application has the breviary which is the official prayer of the Catholic Church. It also has the Missal, readings for mass, prayers and the rites for the Catholic Church. This is a free application.

Websites that every catholic should visit:

- The Vatican website. This website has all the documents of the Church, the Bible, the Catechism and information and news from Pope Francis. This would be call the official webpage of the Catholic Church in the world.
